{"tid":1929962,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】我想問吓設計師可以點較個對焦先可以射到政權","createTime":"2020-03-17T09:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T05:16:17.000Z","uid":108972,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"92c0c2d78d8c1f1ec4336fd20ee591a32c6c7192","tid":1929962,"uid":108972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T09:00:00.000Z","msg":"Hard Sell系列之「冇錯又係我呀」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好意思其實我都好鍾意攝影，希望同大家暢所欲言討論攝影之前，誠意各位設計師加入屬於你哋嘅工會！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位設計師！唔講你唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屬於你哋嘅工會正式上線啦！<br />\n仲唔快啲加入保障自己嘅勞工權益<br />\n並且為到香港出一分力<br />\n<br />\n香港設計職人工會會員申請表格連結：<br />\n <a href=\"https://forms.gle/jj6gcrk42i3mtafx9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fjj6gcrk42i3mtafx9&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8Le6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=ca508b32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/jj6gcrk42i3mtafx9</a><br />\n<br />\n仲有其他渠道可以接觸我哋<br />\n========================⁣<br />\n香港設計職人工會：⁣<br />\nHP : <a href=\"https://hkdiu.design\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkdiu.design&d=AC0Zr9jWFF2OJ189utQw8Le6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=58d5c501\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkdiu.design</a>⁣⁣⁣<br />\nTG : <a href=\"https://t.me/hkdiu⁣⁣